<lb n="0216b20" ed="T"/>吠<note place="inline">引</note>毘藥<note place="inline">二合</note>娑嚩<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0215020"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">引二</rdg></app>合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十</note></p>
<lb n="0216b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0216b2101">我今說根本印。以二手右押左內相叉。竪二
<lb n="0216b22" ed="T"/><note n="0216031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">名＝右【三】</note><note n="0216031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名【大】，右【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0216031"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">右</rdg></app>指頭相合。屈二頭指如鉤。若迎請時向身
<lb n="0216b23" ed="T"/>招。若發遣時向外撥。念誦時結印當心誦七
<lb n="0216b24" ed="T"/>遍即頂上散。然後取念珠專注念誦。次說吉
<lb n="0216b25" ed="T"/>祥天女身印。二手虛心合掌。開二頭指二中
<lb n="0216b26" ed="T"/>指二無名指。屈如蓮華形。二大指二小指<note n="0216032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">竪＝堅【明】</note><note n="0216032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">竪【大】，堅【明】</note><app n="0216032"><lem wit="【大】">竪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">堅</rdg></app>
<lb n="0216b27" ed="T"/>合。若念誦時當心結誦真言七遍頂上<note n="0216033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">散＋（毘沙門天王經中）【三】【乙】</note><note n="0216033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">散【大】，散毘沙門天王經中【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0216033"><lem wit="【大】">散</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">散毘沙門天王經中</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0216b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0216b2801"><note n="0216034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">毘字以下甲本無</note><note n="0216034" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->毘字以下甲本無</note>毘沙門天王呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0216b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0216b2901" cb:type="dharani">那謨裴鑠囉皤拏寫<note place="inline">一</note>摩訶曷囉闍寫施鞞<note place="inline">二</note>
<pb n="0216c" xml:id="T21.1244.0216c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0216c01" ed="T"/>娑婆呵<note place="inline">三</note>施皤<note n="0216035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𧿡＝跋【三】【乙】</note><note n="0216035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𧿡【大】，跋【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0216035"><lem wit="【大】">𧿡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">跋</rdg></app>跌犁娑婆<note n="0216036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＋（四）【三】【乙】</note><note n="0216036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】，訶四【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0216036"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">訶四</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0216c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0216c0201">若呪淨<note n="0216037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">油＝洒【三】</note><note n="0216037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">油【大】，洒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0216037"><lem wit="【大】">油</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">洒</rdg></app>七<note n="0216038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍＋（二七遍）【三】【乙】</note><note n="0216038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遍【大】，遍二七遍【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0216038"><lem wit="【大】">遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">遍二七遍</rdg></app>用塗臥所。乞財物等得如
<lb n="0216c03" ed="T"/>所願。</p>
